      "content": "but i've had panic attacks before and it feels almost exactly like this. i'm kinda exhausted from the flight and just want to sleep it off. is there any way i can just take something to calm down and wait until tomorrow to see a doctor? i dont want to go to a hospital in a foreign country if i dont have to.",
